noticeDescription: Take notice that the Council of the City of Toronto has passed By-law No.1148-2018 to designate 50 King Street East (the Quebec Bank) (Toronto Centre-Rosedale, Ward 28) as being of cultural heritage value or interest.

Bylaw 1129-2018 - To provide for the entering into of a heritage easement agreement for the conservation of the property known municipally as 50 King Street East.
Bylaw 1148-2018 - To designate the property at 50 King Street East (the Quebec Bank) as being of cultural heritage value or interest.
